&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although it doesn&apos;t fail frequently on CI it&apos;s quite easy to reproduce it locally.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the failure is caused by the two tests on the class not waiting for the future returned by &lt;tt&gt;IInstance#shutdown()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
